doc.description: A class to manage Subscriptions gateway restrictions.
A SQL Transaction Handler to assist with starting, commiting and rolling back transactions.
doc.long_description: This class also closes off an active transaction before shutdown to allow for shutdown processes to write to the database.

doc.description: A Initial Cart Stock Manager class.
doc.long_description: Contains functions which assists in overriding WC core functionality to allow initial carts to bypass stock validation. Only initial/parent order carts which have already handled stock need to be handled by this class.
